> =3D <span style=3D"font-family: Symbol;">=E2=88=9A(</span><em>t<sup>2</su=
p> / (t<sup>2</sup> + df))</em></p>

<p align=3D"left">Note: d and r<sub>Y<span style=3D"font-family: Symbol;">l=
 </span></sub>are positive if the mean difference is in the predicted direc=
tion.</p>
